As a Software Tester, write detailed and automation-ready manual test cases based on the user story and acceptance criteria given below. The test cases must be compatible with Playwright and MCP server for future automation.

User Story Location:
user stories path: user-stories/
user story id: 

Use the following test case format:

Test Case ID:
Test Name:
Precondition: [Specific precondition related to the feature being tested]
Steps:
Expected Result:

Instructions:

Include positive, negative, and edge case scenarios

Ensure full coverage of all acceptance criteria and user story functionality

Write clear, specific steps that simulate real user actions and are suitable for UI automation

Keep each test case atomic, focused, and structured for easy implementation

